I'm French and live in Paris. I'm passionate about creation, pictures and design. I recently discovered web development and since then, I try to work everyday to improve my baby knowledge !

I'm absolutely passionate about creating in all forms and I love working on clear and intuitive interfaces.

I am a very curious perfectionist, always in quest of novelties and I constantly try to stay open and keep myself informed about front-end developping.

Here's some of my working projects so far (website, drawings, photoshop compositions), feel free to contact me, I'm always looking for advise and new projects ! 

